<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٤٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يُنظَرُونَ}</span> ... يُمْهَلُونَ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٤١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَحَاقَ}</span> ... فَحَلَّ، وَأَحَاطَ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٤٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَكْلَؤُكُم}</span> ... يَحْفَظُكُمْ، وَيَحْرُسُكُمْ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٤٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يُصْحَبُونَ}</span> ... يُجَارُونَ، وَيُمْنَعُونَ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٤٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{نَنقُصُهَا مِنْ أَطْرَافِهَا}</span> ... يَنْقُصَ اللهُ الأَرْضَ مِنْ جَوَانِبِهَا بِمَا يُنْزِلُهُ مِنْ عَذَابِهِ، وَهَزِيمَةٍ بِالكُفَّارِ فِي كُلِّ نَاحِيَةٍ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٤٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أُنذِرُكُم}</span> ... أُخَوِّفُكُمْ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
